snippet.title: NUGGETS at LAKERS | NBA FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | October 30, 2022
snippet.description:
Never miss a moment with the latest news, trending stories and highlights to bring you closer to your favorite players and teams.

Download now: https://app.link.nba.com/APP22

The Los Angeles Lakers defeated the Denver Nuggets, 121-110. LeBron James led the way for the Lakers with 26 PTS, 6 REB and 8 AST, while Anthony Davis (23 PTS, 15 REB) and Russell Westbrook (18 PTS, 8 REB, 8 AST) added a combined 41 PTS in the victory. Nikola Jokic tallied 23 PTS, 14 REB and 6 AST for the Nuggets in the losing effort. The Lakers improve to 1-5 on the season, while the Nuggets fall to 4-3.
